    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299690/extras/b927241dbcaa37f2f4d6d342d7747426.avif?t=1763436311\" width=616 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平淡的生活中，作为调香店店主&amp;二次元宅女的你经营着自己的调香店，过着简单而幸福的生活~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某日一场突如其来的车祸令你失去意识，再次醒来后，眼前是三个自称“人类灵魂中转中心”员工的天使、恶魔与堕天使男子。你得知自己本应在车祸中丧失性命，却莫名其妙地死而复生。为了调查这一异常情况，他们需要在接下来几天对你的生活进行观察。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在与三人接触的过程中，车祸的真相被揭开，背后似乎还有更深的隐情......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299690/extras/8da800b2c76c5f49627c3a2f8dc13738.avif?t=1763436311\" width=616 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299690/extras/4cfad33d47899247084214b579ed7b53.avif?t=1763436311\" width=616 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：191cm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部门：天使部</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职位：引导者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >香水店的常客，人间职业是律师。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嘴边总是挂着彬彬有礼的微笑，待人接物颇具风度。他和接触过的所有人都保持着得体的距离。总是频繁地来店里光顾，顺便带上送给店主的礼物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299690/extras/4b139eb06eaa438fdb352e84fbec983f.avif?t=1763436311\" width=616 height=194 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：185cm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部门：恶魔部</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职位：引导者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最近小有名气的模特，十分自恋、说话欠扁，有着原子弹一般的社交风格。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为突出的外表以及我行我素的行事风格，总能给人留下深刻印象。做事全凭自己心意，不是很在乎别人的看法，偶尔会有好奇心旺盛以及孩子气的一面。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299690/extras/cd000b79456f3c7fcc40cf1a6077fb01.avif?t=1763436311\" width=616 height=194 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：181cm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部门：执刑部</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职位：执刑者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >执刑部攻击力最强的堕天使，少言寡语的医生。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看起来比较冷漠，令人感到难以接近。但不知为何，在调香店对面的咖啡店雷打不动地每天光顾了近一年的时间。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299690/extras/2134864c9443547a8599faefa623eb6b.avif?t=1763436311\" width=616 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299690/extras/acd80153fe1d0e6f364182f60605def1.avif?t=1763436311\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299690/extras_big/acd80153fe1d0e6f364182f60605def1.avif?t=1763436311 width=1560 height=5632 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·一款奇幻欢脱小甜饼，在轻松喜剧的氛围中享受恋爱！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·全文25w字文本，游玩时间8h左右。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·三段截然不同的恋爱路线。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推荐攻略顺序：陆司华-景棠-洛斐 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·全配音覆盖。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·轻松的调香小游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·多达21种结局（锁线达成三位男主TE后，重新开始游戏即可解锁）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>*【注意事项】</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1游戏中存在部分含有一位<strong>男性配角是双性恋（Bisexual）（该男性配角存在对另外一位男性配角单相思的设定）</strong>的设定和文字表现。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2关于是否能够分享或直播《香恋Ready！》的游戏画面/游玩实况：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可直接分享或直播 (包含“收益化”直播) 游戏前三章内容而无需获得事先许可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >后续内容可以在标明游戏名《香恋Ready！》的情况下，节选片段制作二创视频发布，不可全部录制或直播。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
